Denco Lighting & Electric Ltd is a renowned  electrical company in Quesnel,BC. We are serving Quesnel it's related areas since 1980. We specialize in electrical work, repairs, maintenance and installation for residential, industrial and commercial clients. Our certified electricians handle electrical work in new builds, maintenance and repairs in established buildings and home automation's. 

We offer Basic electrical wiring, Electrical panel repair,Commercial lighting,Electrical renovation etc. We offer free estimates for our services. Our team of electricians considers no job too big or too small, so please call us at (250) 992-5250 today to tackle any project you may have. We are just a call away.
